name: The Consultant
overview: After an unspeakable tragedy at CompWare, a games studio based in downtown Los Angeles, a mysterious consultant, Regus Patoff, blows into town and takes charge.

episodes.name: Mama
episodes.overview: In search of answers about her son’s death, Mama Sang pays a visit to CompWare. Elaine questions Regus’ motives, while Craig makes unexpected headway on a new game.

episodes.name: Friday
episodes.overview: Regus invites himself out with Craig, which quickly escalates and gets out of control. Meanwhile, preparing for a date, Elaine stumbles upon a key to the records room.

episodes.name: Sang
episodes.overview: We flashback to Sang-woo meeting Regus Patoff and their binding contract. In the present, Craig’s still rattled by his night out with the boss, while Elaine makes strides to keep CompWare afloat.

episodes.name: Sick
episodes.overview: Determined to uncover the enigmatic Frank Florez, Craig makes a trip to Pomona. At the office, chaos ensues when Regus Patoff announces a managerial suite is up for grabs.

episodes.name: Glass
episodes.overview: As CompWare’s latest game nears launch, Elaine fears the worst of its effect on consumers. Despite Craig’s efforts at church, Patti feels Regus Patoff’s pull, drawing her from her fiancé.

episodes.name: Elephant
episodes.overview: Days later, Patti’s yet to return home, causing Craig to spiral. Chained to an impossible task, Elaine finds herself calling upon an ex for help.
